.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82841b7ed26acbb7c43b01f64b2bf02c93248a6","tid":390391,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ac96a8a249f022df1d23ed9c8c5af5304467fa","tid":390391,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倒左落模之後 好似啲人「燉」煙仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過用牙籤篤走佢"},{"pid":"b670b1217ffcd55a8eb794b63636a640d4608bba","tid":390391,"uid":95544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"巴打點整個布丁 之前整過 但好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27590aa271372feaa6c05e513800560bb4d2523","tid":390391,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"除左焗之前整走氣泡（如果有火槍燒一燒佢最快冇晒），另外要低溫長時間包錫紙隔水焗"},{"pid":"775bd88f2cdd3d643cea0e4fb1595552d18a06e6","tid":390391,"uid":121361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"用火燒"},{"pid":"3877e19ff7608b13907e5ee74c7a4c7ccf2de1a5","tid":390391,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe2209529386b55709e2b08098356793974731","tid":390391,"uid":97096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"除咗d布丁焗前要整走d氣泡，d焦糖都唔可以有泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要慢慢倒焦糖，有泡要襯早整走，如果唔係硬咗就好難整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}